{"tid":2341504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺最新電話騙案！","createTime":"2020-12-26T12:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T12:19:11.000Z","uid":27502,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de195e8b8fa16ad54a2925b7e270e2962f4c95d5","tid":2341504,"uid":27502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:06:52.000Z","msg":"因為冇人講 所以我講先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日屋企收到個電話 <br />\n一黎係電話錄音<br />\n聲稱衛生署打黎<br />\n話你最近既新冠檢測呈<span class=\"red\">陽性</span>之類之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再廣東話1字 英文2字 普通話3字咁   <br />\n簡完之後就有人聽 <br />\n問你屋企近日係咪有人做左檢測<br />\n<span class=\"red\">話問你拎檢測者既資料咁</span><br />\n<br />\n聽到哩度當然醒目既師兄都知唔對路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點會係佢冇你資料問番你轉頭<br />\n<br />\n但係有時屋企老人家未必清醒/驚疫情<br />\n可能聽到陽性就嚇親<br />\n再比人chok兩chok就講曬屋企人資料出黎<br />\n所以希望大家幫手傳出去<br />\n唔好比不法之徒借武肺呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27cf21e0a07a1495076bae64faaae1f6af93f572","tid":2341504,"uid":219128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:09:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1ace508d645e067deea52e793f775eca1bcf28","tid":2341504,"uid":2403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b9409cd89d786edb103498e2e30ff1b802792a","tid":2341504,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12588d1b69b5ae6ee28ababb0bfd10d9298ef0e5","tid":2341504,"uid":151616,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:18:15.000Z","msg":"嗰日我一做完檢測就收到呢個詐騙電話，屌肯撚定賣撚左我啲資料。"},{"pid":"acce39490f72cc2ab91cd